:: ExampleSim_Start [sim]
<<cacheSimAudio "vomit" "audio/sims/example/vomit.mp3">>\
<<loadAssessmentDefaults "ExampleSim_AssessmentDefaults">>\
<h2>Example Simulation — Start</h2>\
<h3>''Patient Script:''</h3>\
*Hi I don't feel so great.
<h3>''Physical assessment:''</h3>\
<<displayAssessment>>


:: ExampleSim_Start_ProgressLinks
