:: Subjective_Assessment [sim]
!! Subjective Assessment

''Patient Script:''
*I feel really nauseous.
*I feel like I haven't had a BM in days.

/% Example: update findings as the scenario progresses. %/
<<set $cardiac to "HR increases on monitor to 104bpm">>

''Updated assessment:''
<<displayAssessment>>


